<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Multiplatform 2D games with reworked levels]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=16629&amp;p=206879#p206879"><![CDATA[
<em>Zoop</em> is 18x14 on Super NES, Saturn, and PlayStation, 20x14 on Jaguar and PC, 20x12 on Genesis, and 16x14 (with visually widened play lanes) on Game Boy and Game Gear.<br /><br />I think <em>Columns</em> is taller on Game Gear (6x16 to 6x18 as far as I can tell) than on Genesis (6x13). <em>Columns Crown</em> for Game Boy Advance is 7x11.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sat Oct 28, 2017 6:48 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
